convertUInt64ToFloat¶

zserio.float.convertUInt64ToFloat(float64Value)[source]¶

Converts 64-bit float stored as an integer value to python native float.

Parameters:float64Value – Double precision float value stored as an integer value to convert.
Returns:Converted python native float.
